<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 KORUS
 Je shaida bisa tudu,
 Cikin duniya da ko'ina.
 Je shaida bisa tudu,
 An haifi mai ceto

[V2]
 1) Makiyaya na tsaro
 Garken su da dare.
 Sun dubi cikin sama
 Sun ga haske ƙwarai.
 Korus

[V3]
 2) Makiyaya sun razana
 A wurin da suke.
 Mala'iku suna rera
 Shelar  'Bishara ne'.
 Korus

[V4]
 3) &quot; A cikin garin Dawuda
 An haifi jaririri.
 Shi ne mai ceton duniya
 Ƙaunar Ubangiji&quot;.
 Korus</lyrics>
<title>Je Gaya Bisa Tudu LW429</title>
